github)
• RYU SDN controller(v4.3.4): use virtual env for this;
Code:
1. Create a virtual environment: python3 -m venv my ryu env
2. Activate the virtual environment: source my ryu env/bin/activate
3. Install Ryu and eventlet: pip install ryu eventlet==0.30.2
4. Attempt to run ryu-manager –version: “‘bash
ryu-manager –version
5. Make simple switch 13 as a L4 switch.
